<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Local working stub of TOP Core: one root (top:Core) + eight Category-Level Objects (CLOs), aligned to the canonical Apache-2.0 TOP Core at github.com/scientixai/the-ontology-project. NOT authoritative; serves as the specialization anchor and carries TOP's Universal DNA (identifier + observedAt + status) plus the bitemporal + PROV convention vocabulary for the CR-domain build." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "TOP Core (local working stub)" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Agent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Agent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Something that acts or bears responsibility (person, organization, system)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Agent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Agent" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Agent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Core> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Constraint> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Constraint> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A rule, criterion, bound, or commitment that admissibility is judged against." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Constraint> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Constraint" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Constraint> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Core> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Core> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Core> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The single root of TOP. Everything modeled is, ultimately, a kind of top:Core, and so carries the Universal DNA (identifier + observedAt + status)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Core> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Core" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Evidence> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Evidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An information artifact that asserts or records something." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Evidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Evidence" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Evidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Core> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Location> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
