<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Location> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Location" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Location> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Core> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Outcome> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Outcome> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A result, finding, or state produced by a process." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Outcome> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Outcome" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Outcome> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Core> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#ProvenancedEntity> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#ProvenancedEntity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Marker for any assertion/entity carrying the bitemporal + PROV envelope." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#ProvenancedEntity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Provenanced Entity" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Resource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Resource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A persistent material or informational thing that is used or produced." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Resource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Resource" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Resource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Core> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Scope> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Scope> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A bounded context of work (study, arm, population, indication)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Scope> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Scope" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Scope> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Core> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Temporal> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Temporal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Processes, events, acts, and intervals that unfold in time." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Temporal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Temporal" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Temporal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#Core> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#identifier> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#identifier> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A stable, dereferenceable identifier for the entity (the 'who/what is this' of the Universal DNA)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#identifier> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "identifier" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#observedAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#observedAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Valid-time instant — when the fact became true in the world (NGSI-LD observedAt)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#observedAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "observed at" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#observedAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#recordedAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#recordedAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Transaction-time instant — when the system first recorded the assertion (append-only)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#recordedAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "recorded at" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#recordedAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#status> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#status> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The lifecycle state of the entity (e.g. active, retired, superseded) — the 'where in its life' of the Universal DNA." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#status> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "status" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#supersededAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#supersededAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Transaction-time close — when a later assertion superseded this one." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#supersededAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "superseded at" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#supersededAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#validTo> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#validTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Valid-time close — when the fact stopped being true in the world." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#validTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "valid to" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#validTo> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Clinical-research domain core: entities recurring across >=2 CR workflows. Specializes TOP Core / HCLS-core. Scope: oncology Pre-IND -> EOP2. Standards projection target: CDISC (SDTM/CDASH/Define-XML), USDM, MedDRA." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "CR-core" .
