<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#AuditTrail> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Secure, computer- or paper-generated documentation that allows reconstruction of the course of events around a record (paraphrased, ICH E6(R3)). In TOP, the bitemporal + PROV envelope realizes this by construction." .
