<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#CAPA> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "CAPA" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#CAPA> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/core/v1#ProvenancedEntity> .
