<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1/gcp> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/rights> "Independent derivative adaptation of the ICH E6(R3) Guideline. The classes, properties, and SKOS concepts here are an adaptation (structure + paraphrased definitions), not a reproduction. NOT endorsed or sponsored by ICH. The original ICH E6(R3) document is copyright © ICH." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1/gcp> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/source> "ICH E6(R3) Good Clinical Practice (Step 4, adopted January 2025): Principles, Glossary, and Annex 1 (interventional trials). Annex 2 (additional/non-traditional data sources) is NOT modeled in this version." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1/gcp> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1/gcp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Changes made: ICH E6(R3) terms are reorganized into an OWL/SKOS structure, definitions are paraphrased, and obligations are expressed as SHACL shapes rather than encoded text. Each derived term carries rdfs:isDefinedBy the ICH efficacy-guidelines source." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1/gcp> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "TOP CR — ICH E6(R3) GCP definitional layer" .
