<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "An inheritable, provenance-native, bitemporal reference knowledge graph for the clinical-research lifecycle (Pre-IND through End-of-Phase-2, plus site operations). The founding domain of TOP (The Ontology Project)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2026-06-22"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
