<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "OWNED, provenance-tagged crosswalks from TOP/CR-core to external ontologies. Aligns to SSSOM slots (subject_id/predicate_id/object_id/mapping_justification/confidence/author_id/mapping_date); an SSSOM TSV is an edge projection of these. Crosswalks are assertions WE own and curate, never imports of the external ontology." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "TOP crosswalk vocabulary (SSSOM-aligned)" .
