<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Mid-layer specializing TOP Core for entities that recur across >=2 HCLS domains (clinical research, hospital, manufacturing, pharmacovigilance, RWE, commercialization). Seeded minimally; grows by promotion (rule of three). Standards projection target: FHIR, OMOP." .
