<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A human. BOUNDARY-ONLY / PII layer: an identifiable Person lives inside the source/site sovereign boundary. Downstream and shareable artifacts must attach to a pseudonymous cr:StudySubject, never to a Person. The only legal Person<->Subject link is the attested Enrollment bridge (cr:enrolledPerson). Clinical data is PSEUDONYMIZED, not anonymized: re-identification is preserved but controlled (safety / emergency unblinding)." .
